10259 { WebAssembly::int_wasm_trunc_saturate_zero_signed_I32x4, WebAssembly::int_wasm_trunc_saturate_zero_signed_I32x4_S },
10260 { WebAssembly::int_wasm_trunc_saturate_zero_unsigned_I32x4, WebAssembly::int_wasm_trunc_saturate_zero_unsigned_I32x4_S },
10261 { WebAssembly::int_wasm_widen_high_signed_I64x2, WebAssembly::int_wasm_widen_high_signed_I64x2_S },
10262 { WebAssembly::int_wasm_widen_high_unsigned_I64x2, WebAssembly::int_wasm_widen_high_unsigned_I64x2_S },
10263 { WebAssembly::int_wasm_widen_low_signed_I64x2, WebAssembly::int_wasm_widen_low_signed_I64x2_S },
10264 { WebAssembly::int_wasm_widen_low_unsigned_I64x2, WebAssembly::int_wasm_widen_low_unsigned_I64x2_S },
10265 { WebAssembly::sint_to_fp_F32x4, WebAssembly::sint_to_fp_F32x4_S },
10266 { WebAssembly::uint_to_fp_F32x4, WebAssembly::uint_to_fp_F32x4_S },
10267 { WebAssembly::widen_high_s_I16x8, WebAssembly::widen_high_s_I16x8_S },
10268 { WebAssembly::widen_high_s_I32x4, WebAssembly::widen_high_s_I32x4_S },
10269 { WebAssembly::widen_high_u_I16x8, WebAssembly::widen_high_u_I16x8_S },
10270 { WebAssembly::widen_high_u_I32x4, WebAssembly::widen_high_u_I32x4_S },
10271 { WebAssembly::widen_low_s_I16x8, WebAssembly::widen_low_s_I16x8_S },
10272 { WebAssembly::widen_low_s_I32x4, WebAssembly::widen_low_s_I32x4_S },
10273 { WebAssembly::widen_low_u_I16x8, WebAssembly::widen_low_u_I16x8_S },
10274 { WebAssembly::widen_low_u_I32x4, WebAssembly::widen_low_u_I32x4_S },
10275}; // End of getStackOpcodeTable
10276
10277 unsigned mid;
10278 unsigned start = 0;
10279 unsigned end = 736;
10280 while (start < end) {
10281 mid = start + (end - start) / 2;
10282 if (Opcode == getStackOpcodeTable[mid][0]) {
10283 break;
10284 }
10285 if (Opcode < getStackOpcodeTable[mid][0])
10286 end = mid;
10287 else
10288 start = mid + 1;
10289 }
10290 if (start == end)
10291 return -1; // Instruction doesn't exist in this table.
10292
10293 return getStackOpcodeTable[mid][1];
10294}

10480 unsigned mid;
10481 unsigned start = 0;
10482 unsigned end = 178;
10483 while (start < end) {
10484 mid = start + (end - start) / 2;
10485 if (Opcode == getWasm64OpcodeTable[mid][0]) {
10486 break;
10487 }
10488 if (Opcode < getWasm64OpcodeTable[mid][0])
10489 end = mid;
10490 else
10491 start = mid + 1;
10492 }
10493 if (start == end)
10494 return -1; // Instruction doesn't exist in this table.
10495
10496 return getWasm64OpcodeTable[mid][1];
